sentences: Me in Motion formed in Ohio in 2006 and toured extensively around the midwest region gaining support.
In 2008 the band attracted the attention of producer Ian Eskelin, who signed a developmental deal with the band.
Centricity Music then signed the band and bought the masters to their full length in early 2009.
Their first full length album, Me in Motion, was released in March 2010.
Lead vocalist Seth Mosley was involved in the writing and production of the Newsboys' 2010 album, Born Again.
